data = read.csv("../Data/Life-Expectancy-Data-Updated.csv")
data$Region <- as.factor(data$Region)
data$Country <- as.factor(data$Country)
unique(data$Region)
[1] Middle East                   European Union               
[3] Asia                          South America                
[5] Central America and Caribbean Rest of Europe               
[7] Africa                        Oceania                      
[9] North America                
9 Levels: Africa Asia Central America and Caribbean ... South America
region = "Middle East"
data2 <- data[data$Region == region,]
data2
plot(data2$Year, data2$Life_expectancy, col=data2$Country,
     xlab="Year", ylab="Life expectancy", 
     main=paste("Life expectancy time trend for region:", region))
